  "remarks": "\nIn his former leadership position as the First Deputy Chairman of the Investigative Committee, Volkau is responsible for the repression and intimidation campaign led by the Committee in the wake of the 2020 presidential election, notably with investigations launched against the Coordination Council launched by the opposition to challenge the outcome of that election and peaceful demonstrators.",
